attributes.title: High Rollers Aerois #1   Welcome to Aerois
attributes.description: Welcome to Aerois! A brand new campaign in a brand new world with brand new characters! The party is traveling to the Sky City of Gusthaven on an airship, the Sparrowblade. However, their journey quickly takes a complicated turn as they are awoken in the night by a thunderstorm and the sound of battle!
